{"tid":119502,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得五月天好撚正","createTime":"2017-02-13T19:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T08:33:53.000Z","uid":17014,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96845a292c9b5b460efdc5f3eb82100d1b04927e","tid":119502,"uid":17014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T19:40:51.000Z","msg":"講搖滾 帶到人可以跟住個節奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n代表作有派對動物等<br />\n簡直就是為搖滾而生 係新一代rock天團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾Maroon5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講抒情 唱出個種感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全感受到阿信既人生經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如溫柔,洋蔥咁 未聽過可以去聽下 你就完全明白我講緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個FD成日同我講咩rock metal 我真係不屑一笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩One Ok Rock PERIPHERY Linkin Park咁<br />\n嘈到仆街 係人聽既咩 聽到我想扔撚左個耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地怪獸結他solo幾咁勁幾咁型 簡直就係入型入格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nXjapan個啲鬼五馬六咁 邊有得同怪獸比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n石頭 瑪莎個啲唔洗講都知佢地勁啦<br />\n打鼓打到咁輕鬆瀟灑 直頭係鼓界第一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n更不論佢地每個人都咁多才多藝啦 每人都識作歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以話五月天真係完美無瑕 完全唔明啲人點解話佢垃圾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n計我話佢地呢啲人完全唔識音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家說對不對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申:假膠</span></span>"},{"pid":"198716d8900d08800cdf4ac6af7f9e67fb2bbff7","tid":119502,"uid":17014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T19:41:38.000Z","msg":"五月天好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262ad24e7a347e537847f1d8e1a1bf632439fdcd","tid":119502,"uid":17014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T19:43:47.000Z","msg":"召喚五迷"},{"pid":"bd938836c6158afa92f65ac94fd9dcfd2bad10f6","tid":119502,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:01:25.000Z","msg":"聽都未聽過"},{"pid":"95103f6a49b786364d0c6eeaa129c5c8651f3656","tid":119502,"uid":17014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽都未聽過</blockquote><br />\n亞洲天團都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a7be07a146a1a795d3e7da0adcaf08b059ab41","tid":119502,"uid":77606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"x japan 齋玩鼓都玩死你啦<img src=\"/assets/